---
title: Warm Chickpea & Artichoke Kale Salad with Tomato, Shallot-Dijon Vinaigrette & Garlic Bread
description: When a hearty, colorful salad is just what you need, we’ve got you covered! You’ll season and sizzle chickpeas and artichokes in a hot pan, then toss with leafy kale and fresh tomato in a quick homemade shallot and Dijon vinaigrette. Serve it with crispy, savory garlic bread to round out the meal.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f2d95b1e86f3e65846fa12-3ecc38f1.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66f2d95b1e86f3e65846fa12-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/warm-chickpea-artichoke-kale-salad-66f2d95b1e86f3e65846fa12
servings: 2
author: Sara Heilman
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
cuisine: Southern Europe
